name: soybean meal and crude oil production | soybean meal | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/1260/documentation

Inventory refers to the production of 1 kg crude soybean oil, respectively soybean meal (incl. hulls). The multioutput-process 'soybeans, in oil mill' delivers the co-products 'crude soybean oil, at oil mill' and 'soybean meal, at oil mill'. ;[This dataset was already contained in the ecoinvent database version 2. It was not individually updated during the transfer to ecoinvent version 3. Life Cycle Impact Assessment results may still have changed, as they are affected by changes in the supply chain, i.e. in other datasets. This dataset was generated following the ecoinvent quality guidelines for version 2. It may have been subject to central changes described in the ecoinvent version 3 change report (http://www.ecoinvent.org/database/ecoinvent-version-3/reports-of-changes/), and the results of the central updates were reviewed extensively. The changes added e.g. consistent water flows and other information throughout the database. The documentation of this dataset can be found in the ecoinvent reports of version 2, which are still available via the ecoinvent website. The change report linked above covers all central changes that were made during the conversion process.];[This dataset is meant to replace the following datasets:; - soybean meal and crude oil production, GLO, 1998 - 2006 (4144f7d5-8de0-4ec8-98da-04b660220e7e)]

From arrival of the soybeans to the mill through crushing and processing to crude, degummed soybean oil and soybean meal.

This process includes the processing of soybeans to crude soybean oil and meal. System boundary is at the oil mill.
category: C:Manufacturing/10:Manufacture of food products/104:Manufacture of vegetable and animal oils and fats/1040:Manufacture of vegetable and animal oils and fats

processDocumentation.timeDescription: Data from 1998 to 2005, current technology for soybean oil extraction
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Typical oil mill designed for soybean oil solvent extraction (incl. pre-cracking of soybeans, dehulling, oil extraction, meal processing and oil purification), US context.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Calculated as a production-volume-weighted average of the revised local datasets.
